headline: Dow Futures Drop as Credit Market Stress Fuels Uncertainty
summary: The Morning Bull - US Market Morning Update Friday, Oct, 17 2025 US stock futures are under pressure heading into Friday’s open, with persistent fears around credit market stress taking center stage. Investors are grappling with falling Treasury yields and a wave of fresh economic warning signs.
